&gt; Age: 16
&gt; Description: Flash wasn't always called Flash.  He lives in an experimental labratory where they test ice cream flavors (I thought I would try a story that made no sense!) The scientists there tested glow-in-the-dark ice cream on Flash. (Remember, back then, he wasn't called Flash) Ever since then, he's been a weird glowing green color, and they've called him Flash.  Being in a labratory for his whole life has made Flash insane.  He sees things and makes weird noises.  He also is obsessed with cows, and often says &quot;Moo!&quot; for no reason.  He loves to eat asparagus. (I told you he was crazy!)

